
// ==================== API ENDPOINTS DOCUMENTATION ====================
/*
API ENDPOINTS:

USER MANAGEMENT:
- POST   /api/users           - Add new user (username, email, password)
- GET    /api/users           - Display list of all users
- GET    /api/users/{id}      - Get user by ID
- PUT    /api/users/{id}      - Update user
- DELETE /api/users/{id}      - Remove user from list

TASK MANAGEMENT:
- POST   /api/tasks           - Add new task (title, description, status, assignedUserId)
- GET    /api/tasks           - Display all tasks
- GET    /api/tasks/{id}      - Display task details including assigned user
- GET    /api/tasks/status/{status} - Filter tasks by status (PENDING, IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED)
- PUT    /api/tasks/{id}      - Update task
- PUT    /api/tasks/{taskId}/assign/{userId} - Assign task to user
- DELETE /api/tasks/{id}      - Remove task from list
- GET    /api/tasks/user/{userId} - Get tasks by user

H2 CONSOLE:
- http://localhost:8080/h2-console
- JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:testdb
- Username: sa
- Password: (leave empty)
*/
